### USER REGISTER
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Usha",
    "lastName": "BIR",
    "email": "ushamail.com",
    "password": "1234",
    "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/avatars/author.png"  

}

### User Login
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usha@Gmail.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "role":"USER"
}

### reading all articles as user
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles


### Commenting on an article
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user":"698c965349ee23be176fe249",
    "articleId":"698ca6634831f82cdda0cd55",
    "comment": "This is a comment on the article second time."
}






