### Author Login
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ashaa@Gmail.com",
  "password": "124"
}


### Create Article (AUTHOR)
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author": "698c9cbe316f7487ffb7a35d",
    "title": "My life is succesful",
    "category": "anushaa@Gmail.com",
    "content": "124"
}

###read articles of a author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698c9cbe316f7487ffb7a35d

###Update Article (AUTHOR)
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author": "698c9cbe316f7487ffb7a35d",
    "articleId":"698ca6634831f82cdda0cd55",
    "title": "My life will succesful",
    "category": "programming",
    "content": "content of test 2"
}

###Read articles of a author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698c9cbe316f7487ffb7a35d

###DELETE ARTICLE
PATCH http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698c9cbe316f7487ffb7a35d/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "isArticleActive":true
}







###Logout
GET http://localhost:4000/common-api/logout


